These are the instructions to perform an Account Creation using Anchor on Desktop.  This assumes you are starting from the main home screen.
This guide assumes you have Testnets enabled.

1. Select "Manage Wallets"
2. Select "Import Accounts"
3. Select "Import from key certificate"
4. Scan QR Code from OKC (screen advances automatically)
5. Enter the 6 words from your OKC (screen advances automatically)
6. Select "Add New Key for this Device"
7. Select "Authorize"